today wasnt a totally horrible day,,i got up around 930, thinking i was going to my grandparents, so i took a shower so i didnt smell like the band bus, turns out, we didnt go there, so instead, we went to a garage sale in my old neighborhood. by that time it was like 11 1130 and we were the late birds of everything, so we walk around and see almost nothing, then i go to keirsten's, shes the 6th grader now going into 7th grade that i "babysit" and shes taller and bigger than me, so i bought some of her clothes, buy the time it was over, other ppl were just givin everything away cuz they just wated to get rid of it.... all in all i spent 6 dollars and got two pairs of pants, a skirt, a pair of capries, two shirts,,, and then i also got 2 other shirts for free!! yea.. school shopping?... check! so then i got thinking, i kida dont like the jeans,, humm so what shall i make of them i figure im gonna do somthin w/ them, i just dont know what yet, or maybe i do..lol then i went to babysit at 730 and just got home now.. wonderful.. and it hit me (as i was sitting there crocheting and two cats next to me trying to eat my yarn) that school starts on wed!!! and orientation is on mon!! thats crazy ... it came so fast .. but oh well ok im sorry, i probibly bored u enough,, bye
i babysit at 11 till like 3ish she said, then its off to band for the away football game at 5!.. yea band bus

if you really know me, i usually dont cry, but tonight,i have the urge to cry, i have mixed emotions joy, relief, excitement, but then theres also, anger, regretfulness, sorry, and i feel like my head is gonna explode, every thought possible is running through my mind and i cant get it all stright, my head is hot, and my eyes are filled with water, but wen i blink, i cant cry, i just have to think about everything and try to sort it all out.. completely ignore this entire post cuz ill probibly be fine later

if i go to sleep right now,, ill have five hours of sleep before i have to get up again, and i still have to take a shower,, lol fun stuff, but anyways, IM GONNA BE GONE !!!!!!!  im excited, but no one will miss me

hello everyone, band sucked today!!! just to let u all know
 im just sitting here thinkin bout how much i really dont like some ppl in the band all that much, mostly instructors. joe comes up to me and says "here" im like what? he hands me the cock block,and theres me thinkin, are u serious, i told him " ive never done this before" hes tellin me "its just a block u can do it," he didnt tell me how to do much, so w/e and he didnt tell me that id be hearing echos, and he didnt tell me not to listen to the other ppl counting, and all that stuff, he told me NOTHING he said, ok that sucked, i sped up and slowed down and i was off. or somthin, so i asked him, so what do i do. he said fix it, i asked how, he told me just do it. im like ok, i eventually figured that i am a mighty, meaty 5 foot 1/2 inch girl w/ little hands holding this huge block thing, not a good combo, it would like slide out of my hand or somthin, grrr.. so half the instuctors mean well , the others i dono .... sekia gave me a thicker drum stick so it would make a bigger click, and joe is tellin me i suck, chaz is tellin me to not let her down, and everything else is goin on too...brian tells me half time, so i go slower, then he says, "shelby, that was like 1/4 time!" and i was just like ok , kill me now!so then hell was over ,, so i thought, then i started conducting(which i love) then wen were about oh id say 1/4 the way in, i have this big black head like down my throat, it was so weir, brian was like " uve been gettin tips from lauren havent u ,,, i was like no,, he said then uve been watcing her, i was like, well only from last year, he said, well ur starting to conduct like her, and that needs to change, ok ............... silence so i ask him what needs to change brain? he said , it needs to be more fluent, im thinkin, its not that kind of song, part three is very upbeat and tight, not all lagato and stuff, and he was tellin me that my three was bad and everything, grrrrrr, but w/e 
then i had victor, oh god help victor::
victor:so are u like drum major
me: i dono victor
victor:well if ur a drum major, is there a band major
me: i dono victor
just stupid stuff like that, then i have miss alexa bushee sayin, wow ur job looks really easy right now, im shake my head,, and she was like, well at least ur not marching, im thinkin, ID RATHER BE MARCHING THAN DOING THE DAMN COCK BLOCK AND DAMN INSTRUCTORS DOWN MY THROAT RIGHT NOW.... lol then wen we get back to the school, laura and annie and everyone are all like, wow u did good tonight, and i love the way u conduct, im thinkin, OMG lol w/e thanks guys ok ill shut up now,, im sorry this was so long, but i do have to babysit tomorrow morning and danielle, cant wait for u to sleep over tomorrow!!
the mail just came! and my bag was in it! im excited, but then i filled it, it was really heavy, ill try it , if i dont like it, ill use it for somthin else.,... im still excited!!!

! im excited cuz i won my bag on ebay!! what bag u ask, well its a vera bradley bag in nantucket red, it called Vera and im using it as my bookbag ~and my favorite part, i got it for 25 dollars cheaper!!!!!!~ i just got back from babysitting and i got 40 dollars for 2 kids for 5 hours!! thats 8 an hour! 4 per kid per hour! and there sleepin most of the night! (900) ok that ends my excitement. hope u all had fun at band! i wasnt there! but u probibly didnt notice

hey everyone, whats goin on ..
i just had some chicken enchelideas and a cookie <mmmmmmmmmmm> band was ok. i could get used to this drum mojor thing. but thats what im sayin now. well see how it ends up. lol im sure it will be fine . anyways, i wont be there friday night and i was feeling kinda bad but then i figure out that half the staff wont be there either .. tell me how it goes.

well today was interesting, i watched 2 girls at my house for 2 hours, i made them a drawsting bag, braided their hair, painted their nails, made braclets and necklaces, and that kind of stuff, we were about to make our crowns when their mom showed up at the door. oh well then i went to band, marching, rain, playing!!, and conducting!!~ it was wierd, ive never really realized when people are watching you, its weird , because it was weird, i found my self lookin at laura, or jordan, i dont no y, ,,, i guess i just wasnt used to the instructors lookin at me to give their sectoion a tempo... but i guess i have to get used to it:)  now im here, hungry as ever so i think ill eat

this night was kinda pointless besides the point that i added to my body mass yet again due to some ice cream w/ the gurls. lol so the parade was at 7, then i almost went home at 930, then i stayed till like 1000, then we went for ice cream and i felt bad for mrs neaser to take me all the way home so i told her to drop me off at the carnival, shane would take me home. lol turns out he worked a 15 hour double shift so we ended up leavein at like 1100. what fun

just tried on my band shoes, yep they still fit, 6s and they still have a lil room .... now that i think about it, i may not need them this year! wait i might have to, who knows. just waitin to go to band to c all my friends! but that will only last for a whole couple min.s the we have to go march. w/e  chelsea gets to conduct for the parade and i found it funny cuz maddy pulled chels and me aside and said,chelsea is conductiong for the parade, is that ok ,(lookin at me) cuz shes older and ull have more time to do it...im thinkin Y WOULD I CARE! lol i found it humurous
